  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to evaluate the function of the knee after a total
      knee replacement with the VEGA system速.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate patients after total knee arthroplasty in terms of function for five years.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
